So once we've gathered all
this data from interviews,

129
00:05:41,690 --> 00:05:44,174
from resumes, from screening,
we then look at, well,

130
00:05:44,174 --> 00:05:45,090
what do we do with it?

131
00:05:45,090 --> 00:05:47,750
And how do we best try and
look at this information

132
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:51,200
to make the correct selection
choice for this person?

